title: [Femereff's Magic Shoppe]
[Femereff's Outfitting]
description: A simple fauna tapestry hangs on one of the glossy mistwood walls, and a mistwood beam ceiling rises overhead.  Some potted luminescent toadstools sits in one corner of an unfinished wooden floor.  There is a gilded maple table on one side of the shop and an oval-shaped speckled marble counter on the other.
